The /ai/tools/pep8-convert API provides a response in the following format:

200 Success

PEP8ConvertResponse Model - Response to a PEP8 conversion request.
state string
State of PEP8 conversion.
version number
Version of the response.
payload object
A dictionary where the key is the file name and the value is the PEP8 converted code of that file.
payloadType string
Type of the payload.
Example 
{
  "state": "string",
  "version": 0,
  "payload": ,
  "payloadType": "string"
}

401 Authentication Error

UnauthorizedError Model - Unauthorized response from the API. Key is missing, invalid, or timestamp is too old for hash.
www_authenticate string
Header
